Proverbs 2-16 <pb/><t>So <f>ⓥ</f>you will be delivered from the forbidden <f>[1]</f> woman, </t><t>from <f>ⓦ</f>the adulteress <f>[2]</f> with <f>ⓧ</f>her smooth words,</t>
